          <h1>Your Pre-Simulcast Activities Guide</h1>
          <p style="font-size:17px">Our Don Giovanni simulcast is coming to you live at the Santa Monica Pier and La Mirada Community Regional Park this Saturday, and we wanted to share a few of the ways you can spend your day before settling down for opera under the stars.The simulcast is a wonderful opportunity to connect with and support the local community. Santa Monica and La Mirada both boast rich cultural scenes, and there's sure to be something going on that will catch your eye. Take a look at our suggestions by clicking the link below!</p>
        </mj-text>
