          <mj-text align="left" font-size="15.5px" line-height="1" padding="4.5px">
            <h1 style="font-size:24px">Join 30 Club for $30 Tickets</h1>
            <p>
              LA Opera's 30 Club makes tickets more accessible than ever! Here's how it works: for each performance, we reserve 30 seats in our illustrious Founders Circle (a value of over $150 each) and offer them to 30 Club members (must be 30 years old or younger) for just $30. Keep an eye out for an email from us 2-4 weeks before a show with an exclusive promo code that you can use for up to two tickets.
            </p>
